<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="440" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,865,1180]" pageId="9" pageNumber="440">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1117,1143]" pageId="9" pageNumber="440">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species has not been reported since 
<bibRefCitation author="Kamiya, H." box="[771,940,1117,1144]" pageId="9" pageNumber="440" pagination="97 - 122" refId="ref16301" refString="Kamiya, H. (1965) Coccinellid-Fauna of the Ryukyu Islands, south of the Amami Group (Coleoptera). Kontyu, 33 (1), 97 - 122." type="journal article" year="1965">Kamiya (1965)</bibRefCitation>
described it from Ryukyus Islands. The 
<typeStatus box="[1388,1436,1118,1144]" pageId="9" pageNumber="440">type</typeStatus>
specimens are deposited in the collection of the Entomological Laboratory, Kyushu University, 
<collectingCountry box="[1222,1289,1154,1180]" name="Japan" pageId="9" pageNumber="440">Japan</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
